               <code code="34068-7" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="DOSAGE &amp; ADMINISTRATION SECTION"/>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Recommended use: thin or fragile, ill-treated hair, malnourished scalp or hair roots, Alopecia, hair loss due to cycle change.</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Directions: must be applied directly to the scalp and then massage very gently until the product is absorbed</paragraph>
               </text>
