               <text>
                  <paragraph>This is a liquid prepared with the technology needed to provide the hair follicle absorption of the active ingredients, plus inactive ingredients contribute to the regeneration of the hair fiber by providing a strengthening therefore. No adverse effects were seen with the use of this product as inactive ingredients do not cause skin hypersensivity.</paragraph>
